---
title: "Glucose Processing: Mgdl Resolution"
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Glucose payload arrives]) --> HasBoth{Both smoothedMgdl\nand unsmoothedMgdl\npresent?}

    HasBoth -->|Yes| BothPref{Tenant preference?}
    BothPref -->|Smoothed| BothSmoothed[Mgdl = smoothedMgdl]
    BothPref -->|Unsmoothed| BothUnsmoothed[Mgdl = unsmoothedMgdl]
    BothPref -->|Not set| BothDefault["Mgdl = payload mgdl\n(or smoothedMgdl if no mgdl)"]

    HasBoth -->|No| HasProcessing{glucoseProcessing\nresolved?}

    HasProcessing -->|Smoothed| SlotSmoothed["SmoothedMgdl = payload mgdl\nUnsmoothedMgdl = null\nMgdl = payload mgdl"]
    HasProcessing -->|Unsmoothed| SlotUnsmoothed["SmoothedMgdl = null\nUnsmoothedMgdl = payload mgdl\nMgdl = payload mgdl"]
    HasProcessing -->|No / Unknown| Unknown["SmoothedMgdl = null\nUnsmoothedMgdl = null\nMgdl = payload mgdl"]

    BothSmoothed --> Store
    BothUnsmoothed --> Store
    BothDefault --> Store
    SlotSmoothed --> Store
    SlotUnsmoothed --> Store
    Unknown --> Store([Write to sensor_glucose])
